eatured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-1mJ","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":19450,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/03\/fasting-ramadan-three-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":5253,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Fasting Ramadan, three days a month","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting the month of patience, which is Ramadan, and three days from every month is like fasting the entire year.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2408 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15098,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/16\/niyyah-obligatory-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":5253,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Making intention before days of obligatory fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Hafsa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever does not have the intention to fast before dawn, there is no fasting for him.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"The meaning according to the people of knowledge is that the fast is invalid if intention is not made before sunrise\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27600,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/fast-monday-three-per-month\/","url_meta":{"origin":5253,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: Fasting on Monday, three days a month","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked about fasting on Monday. The Prophet said, \u201cThat is the day I was born and the day I was sent with revelation. Fasting three days of every month and Ramadan after Ramadan is like fasting for a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1641,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/11\/27\/best-after-ramadan-muharram\/","url_meta":{"origin":5253,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Best fast after Ramadan is Muharram","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best prayer after the prescribed prayers is a prayer offered in the middle of the night. The best fast after the month of Ramadan is fasting in the month of Allah, al-Muharram.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5250,"url":"https:\/\/ww